      <h1>How to Partner With Your Video Agency to Drive Sales</h1>
      <p class="lead">Learn how to structure your video agency partnership to drive sales and strengthen customer engagement, with a Siemens case study.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>October 16, 2024</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 24, 2025</span></p>
    </div>
